{
  "3204720": {
    "name": "Veilwalkers",
    "steam_appid": 3204720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/09bec5b76c1d517c59c38220f2b52590.avif?t=1753672228\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Veilwalkers》是一款黑暗氛围浓厚的类Roguelike卡牌构筑游戏，每打出一张卡牌都能积累战斗节奏——但每一个错误也可能是你最后的失误。带领一队被诅咒的英雄穿越不断变化的异界领域，掌握强大的卡牌、遗物与祝福，在回合制战斗中对抗邪异恐怖与堕落敌人。制定策略，不断适应，一张卡一张卡地深入未知世界。你能打破迷雾的封锁，还是将被它吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>迷雾已经腐化了整个世界……</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/ca355f4fe74ce49c45bdab106a6ec782.poster.avif?t=1753672228\" width=1056 height=594 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/ca355f4fe74ce49c45bdab106a6ec782.webm?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/ca355f4fe74ce49c45bdab106a6ec782.mp4?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界已被迷雾之尘腐化，野生生物变成了凶残而堕落的怪兽。如今，新的危险敌人在世界各地游荡！正因如此，被诅咒的英雄们挺身而出，肩负起清除这些生物、恢复昔日和平王国的平衡与秩序的重任！整装待发，准备迎战迷雾及其所有的腐化吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>整装待发，向迷雾反击……</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/6d22b695252effd704406f7d2597bb64.poster.avif?t=1753672228\" width=1036 height=582 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/6d22b695252effd704406f7d2597bb64.webm?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/6d22b695252effd704406f7d2597bb64.mp4?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这个世界充满危险。你必须用在冒险途中找到的各种装备来武装你的英雄！<br>装备能提升英雄对抗怪物时的战斗效率。你为英雄选择的装备将决定他们的命运与生存之道！<br>直面这些怪物，不断变强，终结迷雾之尘带来的腐化，让王国重获安宁！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>升级你的卡牌……</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/1760226e445b81f80edab52d10c99ad6.poster.avif?t=1753672228\" width=1056 height=594 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/1760226e445b81f80edab52d10c99ad6.webm?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/1760226e445b81f80edab52d10c99ad6.mp4?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的卡牌将决定你的每 次挑战是成功还是失败！迷雾之尘或许制造了敌人，但也孕育了盟友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前往迷雾法师处升级你的卡牌，让它们变得更强大！只有这样，你才能在接下来的旅程中有机会战胜前方的敌人！在旅途中邂逅更多卡牌，构筑你的卡组，击败那些最强大的敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>在旅途中寻找卡牌与装备……</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/7e816791baad1f9f2d296a2e89ddf05a.poster.avif?t=1753672228\" width=1536 height=864 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/7e816791baad1f9f2d296a2e89ddf05a.webm?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204720/extras/7e816791baad1f9f2d296a2e89ddf05a.mp4?t=1753672228\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有灾难的地方，总有人试图从中牟利！些旅行商人游走在危险的森林中，出售你旅途中可以使用的装备和卡牌！务必留意这些人，获取能让你在旅程中变得更强的物品！</p>",
